Fairfax Financial - Wikipedia






















 






Fairfax Financial

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Fairfax Financial Holdings Ltd.)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Fairfax Financial Holdings Limited





Type

Public


Traded as
TSX: FFH
TSX: FFH.U
OTCQB: FRFHF


Industry
Insurance


Founded
1985


