DRIVING DIRECTIONS
The following driving directions are from the Toronto Pearson International Airport.

When exiting the airport take the Highway 427 South ramp. 
Merge onto Provincial Route 427 South. 
Merge onto Gardiner Expressway East via the left exit. 
Take the Highway-11A/York ramp toward Bay North. 
Take the York Street ramp. 
Stay straight to go onto York Street/Provincial Route 11A. Continue to follow York Street. 
Turn right onto Piper Street. 
Turn left onto Wellington Street West. 
